title: Elizabeth D’Alessio
text:
About
Hello, I’m Liz. I’m a freelance photographer, communications coordinator, and economics student living in Winnipeg, Manitoba. Artistic expression, information deep-dives, and figuring out what makes things tick are what light me up.
